{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "85b53383-9259-40e8-8089-18ade6a09060", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/85b53383-9259-40e8-8089-18ade6a09060@3.pkg/1772597516669/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597517264", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/85b53383-9259-40e8-8089-18ade6a09060@3.pkg/1772597516669/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597517264"}, "identifier": "85b53383-9259-40e8-8089-18ade6a09060", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<p>一审题干；二审设问；三审题肢。</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<p>①：国家工作人员就职时依照法律规定公开进行宪法宣誓是国家工作人员就职时的一种仪式，旨在表达他们对宪法的尊重和忠诚。与宪法监督无关，故①不符合题意；</p>\n\n<p>②：全国人大作为最高国家权力机关，对宪法进行的修改行为。体现了全国人大行使立法权，故②不符合题意；</p>\n\n<p>③：对行政法规、地方性法规进行合宪性审查，属于宪法监督的核心内容，故③符合题意；</p>\n\n<p>④：因违宪撤销地方规定，直接体现宪法监督的效力，故④符合题意；</p>\n\n<p>故本题选D。</p>\n"}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<p>（改编·2025广西中考真题）加强宪法监督有利于维护宪法权威。下列选项能体现宪法监督的是（&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;）</p>\n\n<p>①国家工作人员就职时依照法律规定公开进行宪法宣誓</p>\n\n<p>②十三届全国人民代表大会一次会议通过了宪法修正案</p>\n\n<p>③对报送备案的行政法规、地方性法规等进行合宪性审查</p>\n\n<p>④某县出台“企业的用工年龄不得超过60周岁”的规定因违宪而被撤销</p>\n", "title": "（改编·2025广西中考真题）加强宪法监督有利于维护宪法权威。下列选项能体现宪法监督的是（     ）①国家工作人员就职时依照法律规定公开进行宪法宣誓②十三届全国人民代表大会一次会议通过了宪法修正案③对报送备案的行政法规、地方性法规等进行合宪性审查④某县出台“企业的用工年龄不得超过60周岁”的规定因违宪而被撤销", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {"timer_type": "sequence"}, "time_dependent": false, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["D"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/85b53383-9259-40e8-8089-18ade6a09060@3.pkg/item.json?v=1754819524488", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "choice_type": "character", "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>①②</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "B", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>①④</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "C", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>②③</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "D", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<p>③④</p>\n"}], "prompt": "<p>（改编·2025广西中考真题）加强宪法监督有利于维护宪法权威。下列选项能体现宪法监督的是（&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;）</p>\n\n<p>①国家工作人员就职时依照法律规定公开进行宪法宣誓</p>\n\n<p>②十三届全国人民代表大会一次会议通过了宪法修正案</p>\n\n<p>③对报送备案的行政法规、地方性法规等进行合宪性审查</p>\n\n<p>④某县出台“企业的用工年龄不得超过60周岁”的规定因违宪而被撤销</p>\n", "object": {"data": "", "width": "1000", "type": "image/png", "params": {"originalImage": "", "blankImage": ""}, "height": "600"}}], "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878"}, "source": {"container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "tags": ["$M002000000", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "ff8080814371757b014390fcdce504bd", "5136342960", "44bec67a-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "$RE0000", "$M003002000", "5036342749", "$RE0200", "6a74973a-0772-11ed-ac74-092ab92074e6", "$RE0201", "e7bbce2c-0590-11ed-9c79-92fc3b3249d5", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "ff8080814371757b014390fcdce504bd", "5136342960", "44bec67a-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "6a74973a-0772-11ed-ac74-092ab92074e6", "e7bbce2c-0590-11ed-9c79-92fc3b3249d5"], "status": "ONLINE", "is_publish": false, "id"